snippet.title: Best VGM 1876 - Mario Party - Luigi's Engine Room
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 1090 - https://youtu.be/SPBIT_SSzmI

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Nintendo 64
Mario Party (1998)
Luigi's Engine Room
Yasunori Mitsuda
